OL,3,CGivan tells schools to continue
OL,4,Cdelivering RE based on 'holy
OL,5,Cscriptures'
OL,7,FSchools should continue to provide
OL,8,FReligious Education based on the "holy
OL,9,Fscriptures", according to the
OL,10,FDepartment of Education.
OL,12,FIt comes after the UK Supreme Court
OL,13,Frecently ruled that Christian-focused
OL,14,FRE taught here was unlawful.
OL,16,FIn a letter to schools, Education
OL,17,FMinister Paul Givan said that the
OL,18,Fjudgement was complex but had not
OL,19,Fstruck down existing legislation.
