OL,3,CGivan tells schools to continue
OL,4,Cdelivering RE based on 'holy
OL,5,Cscriptures'
OL,7,FHe also stated that Christianity
OL,8,Fremains the main religion in Northern
OL,9,FIreland
OL,11,FEarlier in November the UK's highest
OL,12,Fcourt ruled that Christian focused
OL,13,Freligious education in Northern
OL,14,FIreland is unlawful because it's not
OL,15,F"objective, critical or pluralist".
OL,17,FThe Supreme Court also stated that
OL,18,Fwithdrawing a child from RE and
OL,19,Fworship could place an undue burden on
OL,20,Fthe objecting parent.
