OL,7,FAt the time the Department of
OL,8,FEducation said they would "carefully
OL,9,Fconsider the complex judgement".
OL,11,FOn Monday, Education Minister Paul
OL,12,FGivan addressed the issue for the
OL,13,Ffirst time in the Assembly.
OL,15,FHe said: "Schools should continue with
OL,16,Ftheir practice that is currently in
OL,17,Fplace but we are going to be working
OL,18,Fthrough the various outworkings of the
OL,19,Fjudgement".
