OL,3,CGivan tells schools to continue
OL,4,Cdelivering RE based on 'holy
OL,5,Cscriptures'
OL,7,FThe minister has issued some guidance
OL,8,Fto schools.
OL,10,FIn a letter seen by UTV Mr Givan
OL,11,Fstated that under current law,
OL,12,Fcontrolled schools should continue to
OL,13,Fprovide undenominational RE based on
OL,14,Fthe "holy scriptures."
OL,16,FHe said: "In other schools, the
OL,17,Fcollective worship provided is under
OL,18,Fthe control of the Board of Governors.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
