OL,7,FHe said schools were also "legally
OL,8,Frequired" to hold "collective worship"
OL,9,Flike assemblies.
OL,11,FThe minister also stated that
OL,12,FChristianity is the main religion in
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland, and the judgement
OL,14,Frecognised that the ''greater part of
OL,15,FRE would still focus on knowledge of
OL,16,FChristianity''.
OL,18,FBut he did say the RE syllabus would
OL,19,Fbe reformed and he would set out how
OL,20,Fin the coming weeks.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
